      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear how hopeless you feel right now, but please know that your life matters and there are people who want to help you through this darkest time. The belief that ending slowly or at all would bring peace is not correct, as suffering can lessen with support from friends, family, or professionals. Please consider calling a crisis hotline like 988 now, as speaking to someone immediately can make a real difference in your safety.",
      "source": "target",
